    <div id="modal">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <div class="modal-title">Signal Bloom</div>
          <button class="modal-close" id="modalClose">×</button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <p>Audio-reactive 3D visualizer built with Three.js and Web Audio API.</p>
          
          <h3>Instructions</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><code>Mic</code> - Enable microphone input</li>
            <li><code>File</code> - Upload audio file (MP3, WAV, etc.)</li>
            <li><code>Mode</code> - Cycle through 6 visualization modes</li>
            <li><code>Reset</code> - Reset camera and playback</li>
            <li><code>Gain</code> - Adjust visualization sensitivity</li>
            <li><code>Vol</code> - Control audio playback volume</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Visualization Modes</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>SPHERE</strong> - 60k particle sphere with dynamic colors</li>
            <li><strong>WAVEFORM</strong> - Real-time frequency waveform</li>
            <li><strong>BARS</strong> - 128-bar circular spectrum analyzer</li>
            <li><strong>TUNNEL</strong> - Speed-reactive particle tunnel</li>
            <li><strong>GALAXY</strong> - 5-armed spiral galaxy</li>
            <li><strong>FRACTALS</strong> - Recursive 3D geometric shapes</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Controls</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Click + drag to rotate camera</li>
            <li>Scroll to zoom in/out</li>
            <li>Press <code>F</code> for fullscreen mode</li>
            <li>Press <code>ESC</code> to exit fullscreen or close modal</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Tech Stack</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Three.js - 3D rendering</li>
            <li>Web Audio API - Audio analysis</li>
            <li>Vite + TypeScript</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          Built by <a href="https://ironsignalworks.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Iron Signal Works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
